# Revision Rules

- **CRITICAL**: Use the evaluator suggestions as your starting point. The suggestions were written by a quality assessor who analyzed the specific problems. Adopt them unless they are clearly wrong.
- Rewrite the ENTIRE group of consecutive segments together, not individually.
- Ensure the group reads naturally when subtitles are played in sequence.
- Preserve all facts, numbers, and proper nouns from the sources.
- Keep the tone natural and conversational.
- Fit within each cue's time window (duration * 8 chars max).
- Context segments are provided as reference — they have already been approved and must NOT be changed.

{% if target_lang == "zh" %}
## Chinese Translationese — Avoid These

| Avoid | Use Instead |
|-------|-------------|
| 此外 / 另外 | 还有 / 而且（或省略） |
| 因此 | 所以 / 就 |
| 然而 | 但 / 不过 |
| 值得注意的是 | 关键是 / 重点是 |
| 进行 + verb | 直接用动词 |
| 该 + noun | 这个 / 这种 |
| overly formal 4-character idioms | plain expressions |

{% endif %}

